    "id": "node_1",
    "text": "Anatomy of a Crime",
    "collapsed": false,
    "children": [
      {
        "id": "node_92",
        "text": "Homicide",
        "collapsed": false,
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "node_2",
            "text": "Murder",
            "collapsed": false,
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "node_67",
                "text": "Malice Aforethought 4 Items - Intent to kill. Intent to do Grievous Bodily Injury. Extreme Recklessness. Intent to commit dangerous Felony",
                "collapsed": true,
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "node_3",
                    "text": "First Degree",
                    "collapsed": true,
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "node_4",
                        "text": "Premeditated",
                        "collapsed": true,
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "id": "node_26",
                            "text": "D thought of killing before hand.",
                            "collapsed": false,
                            "children": []
                          }
                        ]
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "node_23",
                        "text": "Deliberate",
                        "collapsed": true,
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "id": "node_24",
                            "text": "Cool mind capable of reflection",
                            "collapsed": false,
                            "children": []
                          }
                        ]
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "node_6",
                    "text": "Second Degree",
                    "collapsed": true,
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "node_7",
                        "text": "Intent to Kill but not premeditated.",
                        "collapsed": false,
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "node_8",
                        "text": "Extreme Recklessness",
                        "collapsed": false,
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "node_5",
                    "text": "Felony Murder",
                    "collapsed": true,
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "node_141",
                        "text": "Why do we have it? To make felons be more careful doing a felony.",
                        "collapsed": true,
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "id": "node_139",
                            "text": "MPC calls it \"Indefensible in principle\"",
                            "collapsed": false,
                            "children": []
                          },
                          {
                            "id": "node_142",
                            "text": "\"Destroys the symmetry of the law\" People v. Fuller",
                            "collapsed": false,
                            "children": []
                          }
                        ]
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "node_143",
                        "text": "\"One is guilty of murder if a death results from the conduct furing the commission or attempted commissoin of any felonly\" - a form of strict liability for homicide. You don't need to prove Intent, willfullness, deliberation or premeditation",
                        "collapsed": false,
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "id": "node_144",
                            "text": "Felony Murder Checklist",
                            "collapsed": false,
                            "children": [
                              {
                                "id": "node_145",
                                "text": "1. Did someone die during the commission or attempted commission of a felony? If yes Run through the Limitations. If no, Analyze under standard Homocide",
                                "collapsed": false,
                                "children": [
                                  {
                                    "id": "node_146",
                                    "text": "Limitations",
                                    "collapsed": false,
                                    "children": [
                                      {
                                        "id": "node_28",
                                        "text": "4 Enumerated Item - making it first degree Murder",
                                        "collapsed": true,
                                        "children": [
                                          {
                                            "id": "node_41",
                                            "text": "Rape",
                                            "collapsed": false,
                                            "children": []
                                          },
                                          {
                                            "id": "node_42",
                                            "text": "Robbery",
                                            "collapsed": false,
                                            "children": []
                                          },
                                          {
                                            "id": "node_43",
                                            "text": "Burglary",
                                            "collapsed": false,
                                            "children": []
                                          },
                                          {
                                            "id": "node_44",
                                            "text": "Arson",
                                            "collapsed": false,
                                            "children": []
                                          }
                                        ]
                                      },
                                      {
                                        "id": "node_37",
                                        "text": "Inherently Dangerous (Abstract and Facts)",
                                        "collapsed": true,
                                        "children": [
                                          {
                                            "id": "node_51",
                                            "text": "Abstract (Minority)",
                                            "collapsed": false,
                                            "children": [
                                              {
                                                "id": "node_53",
                                                "text": "Could it ever be done without death?",
                                                "collapsed": false,
                                                "children": [
                                                  {
                                                    "id": "node_54",
                                                    "text": "If so, it's not inherently dangerous. Favors Defendant.",
                                                    "collapsed": false,
                                                    "children": []
                                                  }
                                                ]
                                              }
                                            ]
                                          },
                                          {
                                            "id": "node_52",
                                            "text": "Facts-of-the-case (Majority)",
                                            "collapsed": false,
                                            "children": [
                                              {
                                                "id": "node_55",
                                                "text": "Look at how D actually committed the felony",
                                                "collapsed": false,
                                                "children": [
                                                  {
                                                    "id": "node_56",
                                                    "text": "If it is inherently dangerous then felony murder applies",
                                                    "collapsed": false,
                                                    "children": []
                                                  }
                                                ]
                                              }
                                            ]
                                          }
                                        ]
                                      },
                                      {
                                        "id": "node_38",
                                        "text": "Merger Doctrine (Independant Felony) (Abstract and Facts)",
                                        "collapsed": true,
                                        "children": [
                                          {
                                            "id": "node_57",
                                            "text": "Abstract",
                                            "collapsed": false,
                                            "children": [
                                              {
                                                "id": "node_59",
                                                "text": "Can this crime EVER be committed without causing serious bodily harm or death",
                                                "collapsed": false,
                                                "children": [
                                                  {
                                                    "id": "node_60",
                                                    "text": "If yes then there is no merger and it can be reun as felony murder. Favors Prosecutor",
                                                    "collapsed": false,
                                                    "children": []
                                                  }
                                                ]
                                              }
                                            ]
                                          },
                                          {
                                            "id": "node_58",
                                            "text": "Facts-of-the-case",
                                            "collapsed": false,
                                            "children": [
                                              {
                                                "id": "node_61",
                                                "text": "In THIS case, was the felonious conduct independant from the act that caused the death?",
                                                "collapsed": true,
                                                "children": [
                                                  {
                                                    "id": "node_62",
                                                    "text": "If it's the same conduct then it's a merger.",
                                                    "collapsed": false,
                                                    "children": []
                                                  }
                                                ]
                                              }
                                            ]
                                          }
                                        ]
                                      },
                                      {
                                        "id": "node_39",
                                        "text": "Res Gestae",
                                        "collapsed": true,
                                        "children": [
                                          {
                                            "id": "node_147",
                                            "text": "Was the killing within time, distance and causal boundaries.",
                                            "collapsed": false,
                                            "children": []
                                          }
                                        ]
                                      },
                                      {
                                        "id": "node_40",
                                        "text": "Non-felony killing",
                                        "collapsed": true,
                                        "children": [
                                          {
                                            "id": "node_63",
                                            "text": "Agency Approach (Majority)",
                                            "collapsed": true,
                                            "children": [
                                              {
                                                "id": "node_64",
                                                "text": "It's felony murder only when the killling was done by the felon or co-felon",
                                                "collapsed": false,
                                                "children": []
                                              }
                                            ]
                                          },
                                          {
                                            "id": "node_65",
                                            "text": "Proximate Cause Approach (Minority)",
                                            "collapsed": true,
                                            "children": [
                                              {
                                                "id": "node_66",
                                                "text": "Felon is liable for ANY death that was forseeable.",
                                                "collapsed": false,
                                                "children": []
                                              }
                                            ]
                                          }
                                        ]
                                      }
                                    ]
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            ]
                          }
                        ]
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
