                        "collapsed": false,
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "node_72",
                        "text": "No categories. Words OK. Can be accumalative and slow building. From the actor's viewpoint. Partially subjective.",
                        "collapsed": false,
                        "children": []
